---
title: Classic Roasted Sheet Pan Chicken Thighs with Potatoes, Peas and Cream of Chicken Gravy
description: Classic meat and potatoes are revamped in this tasty dinner. Roasted potatoes and sweet red onions share the same baking sheet as juicy roasted chicken for a super simple clean-up. Tender snap peas and a creamy chicken sauce finish off the meal!

